==English==
===Noun===
'''curveball''' (plural: curveballs)

#{{baseball}} A forespin [[pitch]] thrown by rotating the index and middle fingers down and resulting in motion down
#: ''He bit on a '''curveball''' in the dirt.''
# A unexpected turn of events initiated by an opponent or chance
#: ''Life has thrown him a few '''curveballs'''.''

